high_descs: Turn right and go to the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the sink
Wash the knife in the sink
Turn left and go to the drawer
Put the knife in the drawer and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the washed knife in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the loaf of bread on the counter
Pick up the knife that is on the counter next to the load of bread
turn around and head to the sink on your left
Place knife in the sink and turn on the faucet. Turn off the faucet and pick up the knife
Turn left and open the drawer on your right.
Place the knife in the drawer and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife in a drawer.

high_descs: Go to the counter on the other side of the dishwasher.
Pick up the chef's knife on the counter.
Rinse the knife off in the sink.
Turn to the drawer on the left.
Put the knife in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife in the drawer.
